  description="Choosing the right adhesives for cemented footwear: polyurethane, chloroprene, water-based options, and application considerations."
  breadcrumbs={[
    { name: 'Home', url: '/' },
    { name: 'Encyclopedia', url: '/encyclopedia/' },
    { name: 'Manufacturing', url: '/encyclopedia/manufacturing/' },
    { name: 'Cemented', url: '/encyclopedia/manufacturing/cemented/' },
    { name: 'Adhesive Selection', url: '/encyclopedia/manufacturing/cemented/adhesive-selection/' },
  ]}
>
  <div class="mb-8">
    <span class="badge-primary mb-2">Technology Guide</span>
    <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-neutral-900 mb-4">
      Cemented Adhesive Selection
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg text-neutral-600">
      Choosing the right adhesives for cemented footwear: polyurethane, chloroprene, water-based options, and application considerations.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden mb-8">
    <img
      src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1542291026-7eec264c27ff?w=1200&h=400&fit=crop"
